	<title>Inserting code in pom.xml</title>

	<para>
		Now it is necessary to insert the following code in the
		<emphasis>pom.xml</emphasis> (the defining file of this project):

		<programlisting>
			<![CDATA[
			<properties>
				<bundle.symbolicName>panifex-samples-salute-spi</bundle.symbolicName>
			</properties>
			<dependencies>
				<dependency>
					<groupId>org.panifex</groupId>
					<artifactId>panifex-module-api</artifactId>
				</dependency>
			</dependencies>
			]]>

		</programlisting>
	</para>

